@host = http://localhost:3000
@baseUrl = {{host}}/api/v1
@token = Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### ============================================
### AUDIT MODULE - Activity Logging & Auditing
### ============================================

### LOGS - List Audit Logs
GET {{baseUrl}}/audit/logs?page=1&limit=50&action=create&entity=contact
Authorization: {{token}}

### LOGS - Get Log Details
GET {{baseUrl}}/audit/logs/:logId
Authorization: {{token}}

### LOGS - Export Logs
GET {{baseUrl}}/audit/logs/export?format=csv&period=month
Authorization: {{token}}

### USER ACTIVITY - Get User Activity
GET {{baseUrl}}/audit/users/:userId/activity?page=1&limit=20
Authorization: {{token}}

### CHANGES - Track Changes
GET {{baseUrl}}/audit/changes?entity=contact&entityId=uuid
Authorization: {{token}}

### Notes:
### - All endpoints require authentication
### - Actions: create, read, update, delete
### - Entities: contact, deal, account, user, etc
### - Replace UUIDs with actual IDs from your database
